  "detailed_description": "Tankron is a top-down wave survival roguelike in which you fight an ever-increasing amount and variety of enemies. Choose from a variety of upgrades to stand a chance. Discover and choose between different tank specializations to enhance your Build.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Twin-Stick Shooter or Auto-Shooter<br></li><li> 30+ unique Items with interesting synergies<br></li><li> Encounter a boss every 5 rounds to test your skills<br></li><li> 15 rounds with different enemies<br></li><li> 10 different specializations with different playstyles</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121130/extras/ad81108acd0f7e3430f2a3816ed37a8e.poster.avif?t=1668851357\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121130/extras/ad81108acd0f7e3430f2a3816ed37a8e.webm?t=1668851357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121130/extras/ad81108acd0f7e3430f2a3816ed37a8e.mp4?t=1668851357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
